# Templates (`templates/`)

## Base & language

- Extend **`base.html`**; set **`{% block title %}`, `{% block meta_description %}`, `{% block content %}`** per page.
- Current language: **`lang`** (`ja` \| `en`). Switch copy with **`{% if lang == 'ja' %} … {% else %} … {% endif %}`** sparingly—avoid duplicating identical markup twice (reuse one form with translated placeholders/strings).

## URLs & macros

- Use **`{{ get_url(path='@/slug.md', lang=lang) }}`** or `@/_index.md` for home—not raw `/contact/` paths—for correct prefix per language.
- **`macros/brand.html`:** logo, language switch (flags); keep **`hreflang` / `aria-`** semantics when touching those links.

## Third-party assets

- **Pageclip:** `pageclip-form` + submit **`button`** with **`pageclip-form__submit`** and inner **`<span>`** (required for spinner). Do not reuse **`php-email-form`** class—PHP validator was removed.

## Frontend

- **Bootstrap** bundle + SoftLand-derived JS/CSS in `static/`. Prefer existing utility classes (`tokyoscale.css`) over one-off duplication.
- New images: **`static/img/`** (or Sass); avoid adding large binaries without purpose.
